<div class="calendaria chat-release">
  <div class="release-header">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
    <strong>{{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.Title" version=version}}</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="release-body">
    <p class="release-patreon">
      <strong><a href="https://www.patreon.com/3deathsaves" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i
            class="fa-brands fa-patreon"></i> Now on Patreon!</a></strong>
    </p>

    <h4>New Features</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Added <code>CALENDARIA.api.setActiveCalendar(id, { useCalendarDefaults })</code> for switching calendars from scripts</li>
      <li>Chronicle enricher links accept a <code>categories="a,b"</code> parameter to open the timeline pre-filtered</li>
      <li>Chronicle Timeline toolbar gains a category filter popover with toggle options, selected count badge, and clear action</li>
      <li>Climate editor adds an inline pencil-toggle alias editor on each zone temperature row</li>
      <li>Locked-range chronicle views show the date range below the toolbar buttons</li>
      <li>New action enrichers for time and weather: <code>advanceToTime</code>, <code>advanceInterval</code>, <code>advanceToPreset</code>, <code>setWeather</code>, <code>setTime</code>, <code>jumpToDate</code>, <code>toggleClock</code></li>
      <li>New Automatic rest mode (default) advances time using the system-reported duration; old Fixed mode renamed Custom and accepts 0 hours</li>
      <li>New GM-only Print / Export buttons render the active month or full year as a printable layout</li>
      <li>New worlds seed display formats from the active calendar's dateFormats</li>
      <li>Settings show a "&lt;Calendar&gt; Default" preset that follows calendar switches; note viewer/filter/date picker and cinematic keyframes route through configurable format locations</li>
      <li>Weather zones can define per-zone season aliases applied across HUD, calendar UI, chronicle, cinematics, enrichers, and chat</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Bug Fixes</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Chronicle date enrichers no longer crash when a non-numeric token is supplied</li>
      <li>Custom Weekdays no longer return phantom days on Foundry v14, weekday names may be left blank, and the settings panel renders again</li>
      <li>Fixed weekday math drifting after intercalary festivals; intercalary-month cells now labeled with the month name (BigCal) or first letter (MiniCal) plus tooltip</li>
      <li>Moon brightness contribution edits persist when saving the calendar editor</li>
      <li>Moon phases stay aligned across HUD, sun-dial, enrichers, and darkness lighting by honoring yearZero, referencePhase, cycleDayAdjust, and reset anchors</li>
      <li>Multi-day reminders fire on the correct day for offsets greater than 24 hours, with check frequency tightened to 1 game-minute</li>
      <li>Weather presets with relative tempMin/tempMax modifiers (e.g. <code>61+</code>) now fire correctly and extend the temperature range outside season bounds</li>
    </ul>

  </div>

  <a class="open-note" href="{{repoUrl}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up-right-from-square"></i> {{localize "CALENDARIA.Release.ReleaseNotes"}}
  </a>
</div>
